The Old Man, will go down to the Grave with Joy, by this courſe, which will create affliction to his inſolent Nephews. Not long after Fadrique dyeth, and is buried after a moſt clandeſtine manner; in whoſe place they ſubſtitute Placidus, whom all perſons affirmed to have been Fadrique reſtored to Health and Vigour. Which buſineſs being fully concluded to the ſatisfaction of the Parties moſtly concerned; 
                           Ʋiteli proſecuted his deſign of Travelling.

This Relation diſcovers much of the Worlds Deceitfulneſs, which is frequently defended by great Authorities improved with diſingenuity.
